ind:studyType rdf:type rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:label 'Study Type' ;
    rdfs:comment 'Classification of the stability study protocol. Accelerated studies use elevated temperature/humidity to predict shelf life. Real-time studies use recommended storage conditions. Intermediate studies bridge accelerated and real-time. Stress studies test extreme conditions. Photostability studies assess light exposure impact. In-use studies simulate consumer usage conditions.' ;
